bilingual.source: Look at the map of the town.
Look at the oceans on the map.

list.abstract: 平均动脉压（mean arterial pressure，MAP）是一个心动周期中动脉血压的平均值。 正常成年人的平均动脉压值在70~105mmHg之间，它的计算公式为：平均动脉压=(收缩压+2×舒张压)/3。
Map（Modified Atmosphere Packaging）是一种应用于气调保鲜技术的名词。该名词常使用在食品包装领域。可能可以在食品包装袋中看到。

yingyinNormal.en: See, every known map registers it as empty desert.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所有已知地图上那里都是沙漠。

yingyinNormal.en: Would anyone like to do the map reading? I will. Are you sure, Daddy Pig? I'm very good at map reading. Oh, this map is a bit difficult.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有人能来帮忙看看地图吗？我来。你确定吗猪爸爸？看地图我可是很在行的，噢...这张地图好像有点难懂啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, look, I don't work here. It's not like I have a map of this place. A map! Good idea. You take me to the map, I figure out where my parents are. Oh boy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听我说，我不是工作人员，也没有这里的地图。地图！好主意。你带我去找地图，我就能弄清楚我爸妈在哪，赞。

yingyinNormal.en: This is the map that shows us where we're going. And this is the map that shows us where we've been. And it's never ever ugly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这张地图会为我们指引方向。而这张地图标记着我们去过的地方。它绝对不是丑陋的。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll map-read and Mummy Pig will drive. Are you sure, Daddy Pig? When you map-read, We always get lost and you get grumpy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我来负责看地图，而妈妈负责开车。你确定吗，猪爸爸，你看地图我们会迷路的，你会变很焦躁。

yingyinNormal.en: Is Daddy Pig doing the map-reading? Yes, Daddy Pig is doing the map-reading. And he's a bit grumpy at the moment. I am not grumpy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪爸爸他是不是在看地图呀？是的，猪爸爸在看地图，他现在非常地焦躁呢。我没有焦躁。

yingyinNormal.en: You are my map. Let's go. Lead on, my map. Show me where we're going.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你就是我的地图，出发吧，你带路，活地图，告诉我咱们现在去哪。

yingyinNormal.en: Mummy pig can drive, and I'll do the map reading. Are you sure, Daddy pig? We always get lost when you do the map reading. We won't get lost.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪妈妈你开车。我来帮大家看地图。你确定吗，猪妈妈？每次你只要看地图，我们就会迷路。我们这次不会迷路了。

yingyinNormal.en: The map to Skywalker. We know you found it. And now you're going to give it to the First Order.
yingyinNormal.zh: 天行者所在位置的地图，我们知道在你身上，现在你要将这份地图上交给第一秩序。

yingyinNormal.en: A map. To Skywalker himself? You are right back in the mess.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一张能找到天行者的地图？你是打算重出江湖了。

yingyinNormal.en: Anthony's not told me too much about the trip. Hmm, a map.
yingyinNormal.zh: 安东尼没告诉我太多这次旅途的细节。看啊，一张地图。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《大卫·贝克汉姆：探索未知之境》

yingyinNormal.en: Shut up. I solved it. Those are map coordinates. Got them. Let's go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 闭嘴，我解出来了，这些是地图坐标。知道了，走。

yingyinNormal.en: There's no side tunnels, no maintenance tunnels. Nothing on any map. Nothing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有支线，没有维修道，地图上什么都没有。

yingyinNormal.en: So what we did was map out the entire room to identify every squeak.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们给整间房做了地图标记，确定了所有吱吱声的所在。

yingyinNormal.en: It's an old map. A speed. Poor dear didn't even know what it was.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只不过是一张老地图，一个罗盘，那老家伙都不知道那是什么。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I was trying to figure out how to get to Buckingham Palace, right? So, I'm in my map and... Hey.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想去白金汉宫就进入地图，然后…

yingyinNormal.en: It is very doubtful that R2 would have the rest of the map in his backup data.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谁都不能肯定R2的备份数据里有剩余的地图信息。

yingyinNormal.en: Who else knows of this map? No one, but Byamba, myself, and its creator.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有谁知道这幅地图？就只有宾巴，我，还有此图的绘制者。

yingyinNormal.en: Every ship has one. A what? A map. What does that say? Tribal Territory.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所有船都有一张。什么？一张地图。上面说什么？“野人领地”。

yingyinNormal.en: Daddy, are we nearly there? The map says, Rebecca's house is on the next hill.
yingyinNormal.zh: 爸爸我们快到了吗？地图显示瑞贝卡的家就在下一个山坡上。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: American archaeologists spent years systematically <highlight>mapping</highlight> the entire city of Teotihuacán in the Valley of Mexico near what is now Mexico City.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国考古学家花了数年时间系统地绘制了整个特奥蒂瓦坎古城的地图，这个城市位于墨西哥山谷，靠近现在的墨西哥城。

examination_example.sentence: A <highlight>map</highlight> is a drawing of a place.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 地图是一个地方的图画。

examination_example.sentence: Visitors can be taught drawing and <highlight>map</highlight> making.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 游客可以学习绘画和地图制作。

examination_example.sentence: A student recently said, “I thought mind <highlight>mapping</highlight> would take a lot of time to do but in fact it saves me time.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一名学生最近说:“我以为思维导图会花很多时间，但事实上它节省了我的时间。

examination_example.sentence: At first, I would have to stop to imagine and <highlight>map</highlight> a new space in my mind.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 起初，我不得不停下来想象并在脑海中描绘一个新的空间。

examination_example.sentence: But how would I <highlight>map</highlight> my way?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是我该如何规划我的道路呢？
